    "content_id":  "5f483219-ad3e-48ec-afbb-4b0caca34b35",
    "description":  "Academy Ambassadors is a free service that helps multi-academy trusts (MATs) recruit board members with relevant business experience.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"what-you-can-get\"\u003eWhat you can get\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can get help to recruit high-calibre board members (non-executive directors) including:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ea bespoke service to find candidates with the business expertise you need\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eone-to-one advice on the recruitment process\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ea free guide to recruiting for trusts\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSee \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.inspiringgovernance.org/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eInspiring Governance\u003c/a\u003e for help recruiting governors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"who-can-use-the-service\"\u003eWho can use the service\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAll \u003cabbr title=\"Multi-academy trusts\"\u003eMATs\u003c/abbr\u003e in England with growth plans can use this service.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"when-its-available\"\u003eWhen it’s available\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Multi-academy trusts\"\u003eMATs\u003c/abbr\u003e can register with the Academy Ambassadors service at any time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-it-costs\"\u003eWhat it costs\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Academy Ambassadors service is free.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"find-out-more\"\u003eFind out more\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAcademy Ambassadors is provided by the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.newschoolsnetwork.org/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eNew Schools Network\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
